text: Huron may refer to: ==Native Americans== * Huron people, who have been called Wyandotte, Wyandot, Wendat and Quendat * Huron language, an Iroquoian language ==Bodies of water== * Lake Huron, one of the North American Great Lakes * Huron River (Michigan) ==Cities and towns== * Huron, California, a city in Fresno County * Huron, Kansas, a city in Atchison County * Huron, Ohio, a city in Erie County * Huron, New York, a town in Wayne County * Huron, South Dakota, a city in Beadle County
title: Huron
